com.oracle.sfp.scripting.api

Interface IIsirRequiredDocsAPI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IScriptingObject

    public interface IIsirRequiredDocsAPI
extends IScriptingObject
    An object which represents a set of required docs. This actually contains a list of documents to be required (which are ALL required) and a list of 'any' documents to be required, which requires only ONE document in a list of documents.
